Package: myprettyreport
Type: Package
Title: Custom PDF report layouts to export ggplot2 visualizations
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Tamás", "Markó", email = "tamas.marko@myhappydata.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: Cairo (>= 1.5-9),
         grid (>= 3.5.1),
         magrittr (>= 1.5),
         ggplot2 (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests: magick (>= 1.9),
          patchwork,
          knitr,
          rmarkdown
Description: This package helps to export ggplot2 graphs into a good-looking PDF file in a clear and easy way with a wide range of flexibility. It has a modular structure so the report elements can be combined in many ways. See the project website for more information.
